[_Siberian Light_](http://siberianlight.net/medvedev-dancing/), [_Global
Chaos_](http://lena-globalchaos.blogspot.com/2011/04/medvedev-stuck-
in-90s.html) and [_Russia!_](http://readrussia.com/blog/politics/00339/) are
among those who comment on a YouTube [video of President Dmitry Medvedev
dancing](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S6Ksc7R6jhc&feature=youtu.be) to the
Russian pop song “American Boy” at a college reunion party a year ago. On
Twitter, Medvedev ([@MedvedevRussia](https://twitter.com/#!/MedvedevRussia))
[comments](https://twitter.com/#!/MedvedevRussia/status/60690193451200512)
(RUS) on the video himself, in reply to Zaporozhye-based fashion blogger
Anastacia Ukhova ([@Halfblood_Uliss](http://twitter.com/Halfblood_Uliss)), who
[writes](https://twitter.com/#!/Halfblood_Uliss/status/60625652239446016)
(RUS) that Medvedev dances like her father.

